description:
Danny welcomes June Diane Raphael to Everything Iconic to talk about her new film, The High Note, and to break down everything going on within the world of Bravo. They discuss the additions of Garcelle and Sutton on RHOBH, Erika and Tom Girardi's love language, RHOC without Vicki and Tamra, and so much more.


June Diane Interview: 3:48ish
